The point system used for requesting translation on Flitto Crowdsourced translation will be modified and activated. 1. Lower limits for setting points will be implemented. 2. Recommended points will change depending on source language. 3. Spacing special characters and punctuation marks will no longer be included in the number of characters. 4. Implementation of point system based on number of words. If you have any questions regarding this modification please contact help flitto.com for more information.

New Level System! Coming this October 1. Each language pair will have its own level. For example level of English to Chinese will be separately managed from level of Chinese to English . 2. Crowdsourced Translators and 1:1 Pro Translators will be distinctly separated. 1:1 Pro Translators who are more able to provide quality translations will be regarded a higher level to Crowdsourced Translators. Crowdsourced Translator of a given language pair can start from Level 1 and reach all the way up to Level 4. However the only way to become a 1:1 Pro Translator of any language pair is to pass the Pro translation test. Please note that you do not have to be a Crowdsourced Translator to apply for 1:1 Pro translation test. In fact if you pass the translation test of a language pair right from the beginning you will become a 1:1 Pro Translator from that very moment. 3.
